<p><h3><A name="intro">Introduction</A></h3>
This User Agreement, the eAuction User Privacy Notice and all policies posted on our sites set out the terms on which eAuction offers you access to and use of our sites, services, applications and tools (collectively Services). You can find an overview of our policies here. All policies and the eAuction User Privacy Notice are incorporated into this User Agreement. You agree to comply with all the above when accessing or using our Services. You are entering into a contract with eAuction address Oxford Road Manchester M13 9PL company number 123456789 , VAT number 123456798, business licence number 123456789.</p><br>

<p><h3><A name="about">About eAuction</A></h3>
eAuction does not have possession of anything listed or sold through eAuction. The contract for the sale is directly between buyer and seller. While we may provide pricing, postage, drafting and other guidance in our Services, such guidance is solely informational and you may decide to follow it or not. eAuction does not review users' listings or content. While we may help facilitate the resolution of disputes through various programmes, eAuction has no control over and does not guarantee the existence, quality, safety or legality of items advertised, the truth or accuracy of users' content, listings or feedback, the ability of sellers to sell items, the ability of buyers to pay for items, or that a buyer or seller will actually complete a transaction or return an item.

Under the eAuction Money Back Guarantee if we resolve a case in the buyer's favour, we may remove funds from the seller's PayPal account to reimburse the buyer for the cost of the item and the original postage cost in accordance with the seller's authorisation provided to us under this.</p><br>

